ACP - Academ.org control panel for Linux and BSD systems
Helps users of Academ.Org network to watch their traffic and money usage, to turn on/off internet, etc.
This program uses stat.academ.org API
------
To start ACP without installing run reconf script. This will change all pathes in bin/acp to relative. Then command to start will: bin/acp 
To revert run reconf again

To build deb package for debian/ubuntu run build_deb script
